data.description: *Due to multiple offers, the sellers are requesting highest and best to be submitted by 5 PM on Monday 2/5/24.* Three bedrooms PLUS office! Welcome to beautifully updated 217 Stratford Drive which features mature trees, large front yard and lovely front porch. Oversized double doors create a grand entry revealing an open floor plan with dedicated spaces. Upon entering, the separate office sits to the left and boasts its own rolling barn doors with beautiful windows.  Back in the great room you'll find beamed ceiling, shiplapped accent wall, a large floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace, and durable wood-look flooring that extends throughout the whole house; no carpet anywhere!The upgraded kitchen boasts bright bay windows that look into the fenced backyard. White shaker cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances will inspire your inner chest. The laundry room sits off the kitchen dining area and serves as an access to the attached garage. Back in the home, you'll find all three bedrooms off the main hallway with nice sized closets. The primary suite features a rolling barn door, walk-in closet, tile shower, dual vanities, recessed can lighting and tile floors. Plus enjoy the easy maintenance with an encapsulated crawlspace. Kings Grant offers many amenities including tennis court, marina, clubhouse, swimming pool, clubs and committees. This home is centrally located in DD2 school district, close to shopping, restaurants, boat landings just a short drive to downtown and the beaches. Schedule your showing today!
